{"tid":332610,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人買過歐洲郵輪啲package?","createTime":"2017-07-23T06:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T15:43:37.000Z","uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"248bd0e34f3a843f30621358b9b0c79059fe7224","tid":332610,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:24:35.000Z","msg":"想試下郵輪trip，但又唔想去亞洲地區<br />\n（之前老豆老母海洋航行者話成船大部分都係蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n年頭工作關係去過德國兩個星期，歐洲環境幾適合我<br />\n行下睇下啲景同建築都已經好開心﹑相反我對shopping手信之類都冇乜興趣<br />\n（最鍾意行教堂﹑城堡同埋啲冇乜人識既town﹑好似帶我去左中世紀咁﹑遊戲背景咁靚.....基本上每一條窄街橫巷都感受到歷史既味道.....做步兵亂咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n所以就醒起好似有郵輪package<br />\n想試下歐洲地中海個trip<br />\n（一般應該係巴塞隆拿出發-&gt;法國-&gt;意大利-&gt;再返西班牙）<br />\n基本上係得航行線上既沿海城市醜極都有個譜<br />\n個人最主要想去左比薩同羅馬先<br />\n<br />\n想問問大家佢package個價錢同實際埋單會差幾多？<br />\n（計埋港口稅﹑其他雜費之類.....）<br />\n有冇心得可以分享下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dddaf36e54313b38269b6e99b1cfecc5c51abe0","tid":332610,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n我之前都研究過<br />\n<br />\n普通航線8日5k有交易<br />\n超抵"},{"pid":"fcd50b307e3fa442053d02c7eb85560f6ddef446","tid":332610,"uid":61512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"歐洲玩郵輪超抵，平過香港好多。最緊要無蝗"},{"pid":"82f544133eb0e617373d872059824e218836345c","tid":332610,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n我之前都研究過<br />\n<br />\n普通航線8日5k有交易<br />\n超抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢寫就寫5k起唧<br />\n我就係度諗緊佢計埋啲港口稅﹑小費之餘此類嘅雜費要多幾錢<br />\n應該冇理由平成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係漢沙機過去巴塞隆拿...再包你除左頭尾兩日既郵輪住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去德國搭漢沙都已經要成6k-8k"},{"pid":"cca1755b398231b6a34cb7eb8459cc0980e3ba59","tid":332610,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐洲玩郵輪超抵，平過香港好多。最緊要無蝗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係諗住離開亞洲地區先玩郵輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前雙親上船過台灣日本玩都話好多蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3cbb479b9acaa2dd0accf3ec91c28583913572","tid":332610,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n我之前都研究過<br />\n<br />\n普通航線8日5k有交易<br />\n超抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢寫就寫5k起唧<br />\n我就係度諗緊佢計埋啲港口稅﹑小費之餘此類嘅雜費要多幾錢<br />\n應該冇理由平成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係漢沙機過去巴塞隆拿...再包你除左頭尾兩日既郵輪住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去德國搭漢沙都已經要成6k-8k</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n稅好似寫明左<br />\n另機票唔明 5k應該只計上船到落船"},{"pid":"c960cbda3973cb5199553bdfb2284fa099837cce","tid":332610,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n我之前都研究過<br />\n<br />\n普通航線8日5k有交易<br />\n超抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢寫就寫5k起唧<br />\n我就係度諗緊佢計埋啲港口稅﹑小費之餘此類嘅雜費要多幾錢<br />\n應該冇理由平成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係漢沙機過去巴塞隆拿...再包你除左頭尾兩日既郵輪住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去德國搭漢沙都已經要成6k-8k</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n稅好似寫明左<br />\n另機票唔明 5k應該只計上船到落船</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://toursimagery.wingontravel.com/Site/Upload/Ark/danzhang/20170703ee9343be-7b38-4754-b81f-680c1c587007.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoursimagery.wingontravel.com%2FSite%2FUpload%2FArk%2Fdanzhang%2F20170703ee9343be-7b38-4754-b81f-680c1c587007.pdf&d=0tGOBxRY4gSQ%2B5tsW92GUBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=abb884d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://toursimagery.wingontravel.com/Site/Upload/Ark/danzhang/20170703ee9343be-7b38-4754-b81f-680c1c587007.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n可以睇睇備註7<br />\n仲未計綜合保險<br />\n另外露台房都要加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加加埋埋應該過萬"},{"pid":"f1e2a6ae63a5b13f95a5e4813016cce36172061e","tid":332610,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n我之前都研究過<br />\n<br />\n普通航線8日5k有交易<br />\n超抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢寫就寫5k起唧<br />\n我就係度諗緊佢計埋啲港口稅﹑小費之餘此類嘅雜費要多幾錢<br />\n應該冇理由平成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係漢沙機過去巴塞隆拿...再包你除左頭尾兩日既郵輪住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去德國搭漢沙都已經要成6k-8k</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n稅好似寫明左<br />\n另機票唔明 5k應該只計上船到落船</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://toursimagery.wingontravel.com/Site/Upload/Ark/danzhang/20170703ee9343be-7b38-4754-b81f-680c1c587007.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoursimagery.wingontravel.com%2FSite%2FUpload%2FArk%2Fdanzhang%2F20170703ee9343be-7b38-4754-b81f-680c1c587007.pdf&d=0tGOBxRY4gSQ%2B5tsW92GUBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=abb884d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://toursimagery.wingontravel.com/Site/Upload/Ark/danzhang/20170703ee9343be-7b38-4754-b81f-680c1c587007.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n可以睇睇備註7<br />\n仲未計綜合保險<br />\n另外露台房都要加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加加埋埋應該過萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來你講緊香港報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港我就唔知了<br />\n我之前係睇cruise direct, 上船包到落船only"},{"pid":"8b6ed5a1beb534576238cb5efe95e62fc93ed64f","tid":332610,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:43:37.000Z","msg":"不過永安口價都幾抵"}]}